🚗 BRTA Services Management System
📌 Overview

This project is a web-based system designed to simplify BRTA (Bangladesh Road Transport Authority) services using AJAX, JavaScript, HTML, CSS, and JSON for data handling.
It provides both user and admin interfaces to manage license applications, road permits, accident reports, and appointment bookings efficiently.

🧩 Key Features

User & Admin Panels: Separate dashboards for users and admins.

Dynamic Data Handling: All operations handled via AJAX and JSON without page reloads.

License & Road Permit Management: Users can apply, track, and update license or permit applications.

Accident Reporting System: Users can report incidents online.

Appointment Booking: Scheduling system for driving test or learning sessions.

Admin Dashboard: View, approve, and manage applications, permits, and reports.

JavaScript Validation: Frontend validation ensures all user inputs are properly checked before submission.

CRUD Operations: Create, Read, Update, and Delete records using AJAX requests dynamically.

Report Management: Admin can generate summarized reports for better analysis.

⚙️ Tech Stack

Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript

Data Handling: AJAX, JSON

Validation: JavaScript (client-side)

Database: MySQL

Development Environment: VS Code, XAMPP

🚀 How to Run

Clone this repository:

git clone https://github.com/your-username/BRTA-AJAX-Project.git


Open the folder in VS Code.

Run a local server using XAMPP or VS Code Live Server.

Open the project in your browser:

http://localhost/BRTA-Project/view/index.html
